<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1016</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yuàn zhǔ de ài chōng mǎn zhè gè de fāng, yuàn zhǔ de guāng zhào yào zhè gè de fāng.
 yuàn zhǔ nà shēng mìng de hé shuǐ, liú tǎng zài zhè gè de fāng.
 yīn wèi zhè lǐ yǒu yī qún shén de bǎi xìng, tā men shì yī zhǎn zhǎn dēng guāng.
 zhǔ bì qīn zì shǐ nǐ men gāng qiáng, zhǔ bì qīn zì mù yǎng.
 zhǔ bì qīn zì mù yǎng.</lyrics>
<title>yuàn zhǔ de ài chōng mǎn zhè gè de fāng 迦南1016</title>
</song>